                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On April 3, 1952, the Paraguayan Government made a payment of $34,372.82 to the
                    United States Treasury in final settlement of obligations incurred under the
                    Lend-Lease Agreement of September 20, 1941 (734.56/4–352). For text of the
                    Agreement, see <ref target="frus1941v07#pg_480">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1941, volume VII, page
                    480</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
